data.description: Wonderful location in the highly sought after community of Sterling Hill with 2 clubhouses, from which one is just a 5 minute walk from the home. Here you can find a small gym room, a resort style pool, playground. splash pad, dog park and volley ball court. The other clubhouse has tennis and basketball courts as well as a separate gym building and an RV/boat parking area as well. The HOA is only $95/year! The CDD fee is already included in the property tax which is still only under $2,800!The home has the best layout with all three bedrooms being separated for privacy. Plenty of closet space for storage and many windows to provide natural light. The property is fully fenced for privacy to enjoy the 12x40 paved back patio.The school bus pickup is just outside the gate.
